cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) tasks such as temporal expression recognition and name entity recognition (NER), which are typically categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper proposes a method to enhance word vectors using prior knowledge from a semantic dictionary, which involves machine learning techniques and could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of morphological information in the proposed method could also relate to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper specifically mentions improvements in NER tasks, which could suggest a connection to cs.NE (Networks and Communications).
